            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Availability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Currently available for:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Frontend development projects</li>
              <li>Full-stack web applications</li>
              <li>MVP development</li>
              <li>Technical consulting</li>
              <li>E-commerce solutions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Timezone</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I work remotely and can accommodate various timezones. I'm based in GMT+6 but have experience working with teams across different time zones.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Response Time</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I typically respond to inquiries within 24 hours. For ongoing projects, I maintain regular communication based on your preferred cadence.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Resume Download -->
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a 
            href="/Updated Resume Md Atiquzzaman Soikat (1).pdf" 
            download
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 17a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm3.293-7.707a1 1 0 011.414 0L9 10.586V3a1 1 0 112 0v7.586l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Download My Resume
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column - Contact Form -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Get In Touch</h2>
        
        <form id="contact-form" class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Name</label>
            <input 
              type="text" 
              id="name" 
              name="name" 
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
            />
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Email</label>
            <input 
              type="email" 
              id="email" 
              name="email" 
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
            />
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label for="subject" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Subject</label>
            <input 
              type="text" 
              id="subject" 
              name="subject" 
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
            />
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label for="project-type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Project Type</label>
            <select 
              id="project-type" 
              name="project-type"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
            >
              <option value="mvp">MVP Development</option>
              <option value="website">Website Development</option>
              <option value="frontend">Frontend Development</option>
              <option value="fullstack">Full-stack Application</option>
              <option value="ecommerce">E-commerce Solution</option>
              <option value="consulting">Technical Consulting</option>
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label for="budget" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Budget Range (USD)</label>
            <select 
              id="budget" 
              name="budget"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
            >
              <option value="under-5k">Under $5,000</option>
              <option value="5k-10k">$5,000 - $10,000</option>
              <option value="10k-20k">$10,000 - $20,000</option>
              <option value="20k-plus">$20,000+</option>
              <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Project Details</label>
            <textarea 
              id="message" 
              name="message" 
              rows="6" 
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
              placeholder="Tell me about your project, timeline, and specific requirements..."
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <button 
              type="submit"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-black bg-opacity-80 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-inherit border-1 hover:text-black hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.5)] transition-colors transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-200 shadow-md"
            >
              Send Message
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
        
        <div id="form-success" class="mt-4 p-4 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-md hidden">
          Thank you for your message! I'll get back to you as soon as possible.
        </div>
        
        <div id="form-error" class="mt-4 p-4 bg-red-100 text-red-700 rounded-md hidden">
          There was an error sending your message. Please try again or contact me directly via email.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Projects I'm Interested In -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Projects I'm Interested In</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Web Applications</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            SaaS products, internal tools, dashboards, and data visualization applications.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">E-commerce Solutions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Custom storefronts, Shopify development, and integrations with payment systems.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frontend Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Component library development, performance optimization, and design system implementation.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Startup MVPs</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Helping founders validate their ideas with minimal, well-crafted products that demonstrate value.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">JAMstack Websites</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Fast, secure, and SEO-optimized static sites with dynamic capabilities using modern frameworks.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">API Development</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Building robust backend services and RESTful APIs to power frontend applications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- How I Work -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">How I Work</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Communication</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I value clear, consistent communication. Depending on project needs, I set up regular check-ins via video calls and maintain daily updates through Slack or similar tools. I adapt to your preferred communication style.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Project Management</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I use agile methodologies with sprints tailored to project needs. I'm comfortable with various project management tools including Jira, Asana, Trello, or GitHub Projects.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Development Process</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I follow a structured development process with clear milestones, regular code reviews, and comprehensive testing. My goal is to deliver high-quality code that meets your requirements on time.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Collaboration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I work well both independently and as part of a team. I can collaborate with your existing developers, designers, and stakeholders to ensure project success.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<script>
  // Simple form handling script - can be enhanced with actual submission logic
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const form = document.getElementById('contact-form');
    const successMessage = document.getElementById('form-success');
    const errorMessage = document.getElementById('form-error');
    
    if (form) {
      form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        
        const formData = new FormData(form);
        const data = {
          name: formData.get('name'),
          email: formData.get('email'),
          subject: formData.get('subject'),
          projectType: formData.get('project-type'),
          budget: formData.get('budget'),
          message: formData.get('message')
        };
       
        
        successMessage.classList.remove('hidden');
        form.reset();
        
        // Hide success message after 5 seconds
        setTimeout(() => {
          successMessage.classList.add('hidden');
        }, 5000);
      });
    }
  });
</script>